title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 59] Coldwave, Post-Punk, Minimal
description:
Dark, gloomy and moody, this is what this torrent is all about. You can't really say these are forgotten bands now as obviously noone knew them back then either. But it does not change the fact that some of the most brilliant music of the 80s was made by such underground bands. Thanks to the internet, they are getting another chance to be discovered.


 
Choir Invisible - Choir Invisible [1981]

Five or Six - Cantame Esa Cancion Que Dice, Yeah Yeah Yeah [1982]

Magic De Spell - A Body in a Snare [1982]

Moral - And Life is [1984]
